    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will not find a single stone chip, swirl mark, or door ding across the entire body. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains supple and dark, showing no signs of UV exposure. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new. The premium leather upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent is still present. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians, with a recent major service including all fluid flushes and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The undercarriage is as clean as the top side, reflecting its life as a fair-weather-only weekend car. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
